                <h1 class="segmentHeading">About <span class="emph">me</span></h1>
                <p class="segmentPara">Hello! Bassam here. I'm an AS student currently enrolled in Nixor College and this is my spare-time-creative-and-technical-and-helpful project!</p>
                <p class="segmentPara">This project essentially started as me being too lazy to send numerous people the individual notes that they wanted. From hybridization in AS Chemistry to Specialisation and Trade in O Levels Economics, sending PDFs on WhatsApp eventually became too tedious. So I made AurParho, essentially a "hub" for my notes, so that I could help more people with less effort. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
