            <div class="mainSegment container pt-5 px-5 w-100 h-100">
                <h1 class="segmentHeading">Our <span class="emph">mission</span></h1>
                <p class="segmentPara">Simply put, to make your life easier. COVID has already had a massive impact on our day-to-day lives. Whether you felt this in the form of added academic pressure, increased mental stress, or the worst of all, loss of a loved one, we have all been deeply affected by this worldwide academic. </p>
                <p class="segmentPara">Hence, AurParho was created to provide some sort of relief, however small and insignificant it may be, from the academic pressure experienced by students everywhere. </p>
            </div>
